d":73148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T06:01:29.000Z","msg":"玩到咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"477d2b260129b1425f0b03a7c4bca2fb290ba4f2","tid":254070,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T06:05:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本唔關肥瘦事 佢個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比你講多次<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/23/140537_f6d0883afd3009441cd5a9465c5e7b4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F23%2F140537_f6d0883afd3009441cd5a9465c5e7b4a.jpg&h=6e50c49b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1644263d0d98fe2f631bc484ac1cf7bc4077655","tid":254070,"uid":107421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T06:06:30.000Z","msg":"評已正<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf165f50e38225d6bc2656f45c6871ce9c2dcb36","tid":254070,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T06:07:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68d55cde3d79c147d59ac0f94adb71cf76d9c464","tid":254070,"uid":18845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T06:09:13.000Z","msg":"正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9528a8d7f5537ef39faa94797d28e50f95d76e","tid":254070,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T06:09:41.000Z","msg":"不能只讓我看見<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1066337ed7e9c894be508f5de5192aae126babb","tid":254070,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T06:10:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85342ae093359531d9f50d178a5268a3833e23a7","tid":254070,"uid":114167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T06:11:46.000Z","msg":"屌睇29+1俾佢個樣破壞晒個心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67bce5bd51d671ae3222eeec97e7722a2d91c4e8","tid":254070,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T06:15:53.000Z","msg":"大部份肥到成座山咁嘅肥婆，條頸後面都好多老泥，因為佢哋沖涼嘅時候卒唔到。 <br />\n老泥俾頸部脂肪一層層夾住，日復日年復年咁累積。 <br />\n所以大部份肥婆條頸都係黑色，越黑老泥越厚。 <br />\n如果你哋有幸溝到肥婆，就人一世物一世點都要試下。<br />\n首先用手指濕少少水起勢咁卒，用匙羹刮出嚟，加兩滴美極慢慢品嚐。 <br />\n初哥可能話核突，但你唔食肥婆老泥等於登上白雲山唔食山水豆腐花一樣咁傻的嗎。 <br />\n<br />\n下身方面又係有學問，肥婆食咁多漢堡包同牛肉，男性荷爾蒙分泌過盛。 <br />\n所以塊西至屎o全部都係毛，無論佢幾乾淨，都有陣咸魚溝變壞乳酪嘅味道。 <br />\n據英國研究，82.5%肥婆都唔會剃腳毛，因為烏低身嗰下等於做sit up，有違肥人忠旨。 <br />\n所以肥婆啲腳毛永遠好似鐵線咁粗。 <br />\n奶西嘅時候叫佢瞓低你忠個頭埋去，兩隻手要掃佢隻腳啲鐵線等佢起雞皮，然後叫佢嗰對火腿夾實自己個頭唔好比空氣流出。 <br />\n陣咸魚味喺真空環境會得到昇華，係有層次而漸進的。<br />\n奶嗰時攝攝聲，有3D立體音響加回音效果。 <br />\n你嗅覺，味覺，觸覺，聽覺得到前所未有嘅享受，呢啲先叫人生啊。 <br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪嗰part唔多講，因為肥婆塊田多肉好撞係常識，你塞咗入去會感受到溫暖同安全感，比一層一層肉緊緊包住。 <br />\n<br />\n成日笑肥婆以為自己好識食嗰啲人，根本就係未夠班，自以為是嘅表現。你比食女界嘅高手揀減肥前欣宜定係整容後楊怡，佢完全唔想答你，一嚟佢唔想笑勁你問無聊野，二嚟佢已經諗緊點班支美極返嚟。"},{"pid":"344490f0d1947a7d4604abef2314a4a1cf6d3950","tid":254070,"uid":85163,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T06:21:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bce86f8b9619970b71d70ccb4b13e7b6d6474151","tid":254070,"uid":92325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T06:23:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://i66.tinypic.com/2a9yyxt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi66.tinypic.com%2F2a9yyxt.jpg&h=fbc1622b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n瘦得有點令人擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03964498926b22b1be5a47bd6f5f7131f4bef3ab","tid":254070,"uid":114111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T06:27:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" cla